{
  "texts": [
    "This could bring about serious consequences on students' mental well-being.",
    "Since the introduction of products like DeepL and ChatGPT, AIpowered language technologies have been steadily advancing towards mainstream acceptance, becoming an indispensable aspect of daily communication and professional routines.",
    "Consequently, they play a pivotal role in shaping social interactions and influencing the generation and dissemination of knowledge.",
    "Nevertheless, this dominance presents its own array of challenges, especially to non-native speakers of English.",
    "It not only provides limited information to non-native English speakers but also poses the risk of developing a monocultural AI that engages in English but lacking comparably low proficiency in other underrepresented languages."
  ]
}